reference "fig:15/2 dist. work hours"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

,
 representing normal work hours noise,
 is typical in that we see that even though the lab environment is in general quieter than the shed's,
 it is not profoundly so.
 See also fig.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
